 {
  "text": "Hi, this is Beatriz. Let me tell you about my week. On Monday, I have an English class at half past six in the evening. On Tuesday, I have a doctor's appointment at quarter past ten in the morning. On Wednesday, I am free, so I rest at home. On Thursday, I have a meeting at nine o'clock. On Friday, I go to the gym at quarter to seven. My favorite day is Saturday, because I have no appointments. I look at my calendar every Sunday night. This is my busy week!",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a4_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hello, my name is Ricardo. I want to tell you about an important date. My birthday is on the tenth of May. Every year, my family has a big lunch at noon. This year, the tenth of May is on a Saturday. We always start at half past twelve. My sister arrives at quarter past one, because she works in the morning. We finish at four o'clock. I love this date, because all my family is together. It is my favorite day of the year.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a4_listening2.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "First, the meeting at nine o'clock. Second, the coffee break at half past ten. Third, lunch at noon. Fourth, the appointment at quarter past three. Fifth, go home at six o'clock.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "pc4_order_l4.mp3"
 },
